Competition: Copa Presidente Adolfo López Mateos 
Season: 1963
BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tablesp/presmateo63.html

* Semiofficial Tournament held in Guadalajara and Mexico City
* One single leg played

Round: First Round

2/17/1963; Club America; 3-0; Tampico; Estadio Olímpico Universitario

2/17/1963; Guadalajara; 2-2 (aet); Morelia ; Estadio Jalisco
Penalty kicks: 2-3

2/21/1963; UNAM; 4-4 (aet); Irapuato; Estadio Olímpico Universitario
Penalty kicks: 3-5

2/21/1963; Nacional (Mexico); 2-2 (aet); Club León; Estadio Jalisco
Penalty kicks: 0-1

2/24/1963; Necaxa; 2-1; Monterrey; Estadio Olímpico Universitario

2/24/1963; Oro; 3-1; Toluca; Estadio Jalisco
* Bye: Atlas, Atlante

Round: Quarterfinals

2/28/1963; Atlante; 2-1; Necaxa; Estadio Olímpico Universitario

2/28/1963; Atlas; 0-1; Club León; Estadio Jalisco

3/3/1963; Club America; 4-1; Irapuato; Estadio Olímpico Universitario

3/3/1963; Oro; 5-1; Morelia; Estadio Jalisco

Round: Semifinals

3/6/1963; Oro; 4-0; Club León; Estadio Jalisco

3/7/1963; Club America; 5-1; Atlante; Estadio Olímpico Universitario

Round: Final

3/10/1963; Club America; 4-1; Oro; Estadio Olímpico Universitario
